OL,6,FA fraudster who travelled from London
OL,7,Fto Rotherham to scam residents out of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds while posing as a
OL,9,Fpolice officer has been jailed.
OL,11,FMichael Smith, 26, pretended to be a
OL,12,FSouth Yorkshire Police officer in a
OL,13,Fscam where he told residents to hand
OL,14,Fover valuable items to him for
OL,15,Fsafekeeping in June 2023.
OL,17,FSmith, of Lady Somerset Road in
OL,18,FCamden, London, took bank cards and
OL,19,FPIN numbers from a couple in their 80s
OL,20,Fliving at Fernleigh Drive.
