OL,6,FHe then went to Cotswold Crescent,
OL,7,Fwhere he used the same trick and took
OL,8,Fjewellery worth #25,000 from a 64-year-
OL,9,Fold woman.
OL,11,FSmith returned to London where he used
OL,12,Fthe bank cards he had taken to
OL,13,Fwithdraw thousands of pounds in cash.
OL,15,FFraud investigators were able to
OL,16,Fidentify Smith by analysing phone
OL,17,Frecords. He was arrested in London and
OL,18,Fwas positively identified by two of
OL,19,Fhis victims.
